---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Sustainability & CBAM Ready Primary Aluminium | Tech Aluminum" 
  description="Learn about Tech Aluminum's low-carbon hydro-powered primary smelting operations on the Nile and complete CBAM compliance ready for European importers."
  lang="en"
>
  <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <div class="container">
      <ol>
        <li><a href="/en/">Home</a></li>
        <li aria-current="page">Sustainability</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- ============================================================
       HERO
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="product-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="product-hero-grid" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr;">
        <div style="text-align: center; max-width: 850px; margin: 0 auto;">
          <span class="eyebrow on-dark">Low-Carbon Industrial Feedstock</span>
          <h1 style="font-size: 3.2rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;">Hydro-Powered Smelting on the Nile</h1>
          <p class="product-hero-lead" style="font-size: 1.25rem;">
            Leveraging carbon-free hydroelectricity from the Aswan High Dam to supply the European B2B market 
            with low-footprint, REACH-registered, and CBAM-compliant primary aluminium.
          </p>
          <div class="product-hero-badges" style="justify-content: center; margin-top: 1.8rem;">
            <span>100% Hydro-Powered Smelting</span>
            <span>Low Scope 1 & 2 Emissions</span>
            <span>CBAM-Registered Importer Support</span>
            <span>ISO 14001 Certified</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       THE HYDRO ADVANTAGE
       ============================================================ -->
  <section style="background: var(--white); padding: 5rem 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cbam-inner" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center;">
        <div class="product-image" style="box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);">
          <div class="product-img-container-inner" style="border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden;">
            <img src="/images/hero/1.7-green-aluminium-production-renewable-energy-egypt.webp" alt="Hydroelectric Smelter Advantage" class="product-img-modern" style="width:100%; object-fit:cover;" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">Assaying Clean Energy</span>
          <h2>The Aswan Dam Hydroelectric Connection</h2>
          <p>
            Standard primary aluminium smelting is highly energy-intensive. Many global competitors rely on coal-fired grids, 
            producing up to 16 tonnes of CO₂ per tonne of finished metal.
          </p>
          <p>
            Tech Aluminum operates a clean-grid smelting process. By direct coupling with the <strong>Aswan High Dam</strong>, 
            we harness pure, renewable hydro-electric energy to drive our reduction cells.
          </p>
          <p>
            This operational advantage ensures an exceptionally clean Scope 1 and Scope 2 carbon profile, shielding our 
            European B2B manufacturing clients from heavy penalties under the EU's Carbon Border Adjustment Mechanism (CBAM).
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       CBAM COMPLIANCE METRICS
       ============================================================ -->
  <section style="background: var(--silver-soft); padding: 5rem 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cbam-inner" style="grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center;">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">Regulatory Readiness</span>
          <h2>2026 CBAM Carbon Border Shield</h2>
          <p>
            Starting in 2026, the transitional phase of the EU Carbon Border Adjustment Mechanism (CBAM) shifts to full financial obligations. 
            Importers must purchase CBAM certificates to cover carbon intensity.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our metallurgy and compliance teams provide quarterly validated carbon intensity data, ensuring your compliance filings 
            proceed smoothly.
          </p>
          <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem;">
            <div style="background:var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 1.25rem; border-radius: var(--radius-md);">
              <strong style="color:var(--teal); font-size:1.5rem; display:block; margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Verified Data</strong>
              <span style="font-size:0.85rem; color:var(--ink-soft);">Fully compliant quarterly data reports for customs filing.</span>
            </div>
            <div style="background:var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 1.25rem; border-radius: var(--radius-md);">
              <strong style="color:var(--teal); font-size:1.5rem; display:block; margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Tariff Shield</strong>
              <span style="font-size:0.85rem; color:var(--ink-soft);">Low carbon density drastically lowers your CBAM tax exposure.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="product-image" style="box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);">
          <div class="product-img-container-inner" style="border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden;">
            <img src="/images/hero/1.6-eu-carbon-border-adjustment-mechanism-aluminium-compliance.webp" alt="CBAM ready primary aluminium" class="product-img-modern" style="width:100%; object-fit:cover;" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       SUSTAINABILITY INITIATIVES
       ============================================================ -->
  <section style="background: var(--white); padding: 5rem 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header" style="text-align:center; max-width:700px; margin: 0 auto 4rem auto;">
        <span class="eyebrow">Circular Standards</span>
        <h2>Environmental Stewardship</h2>
        <p>Our commitment extends beyond green energy to strict environmental and circular management protocols.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="product-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
        <div style="background:var(--silver-soft); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding:2rem; border-radius:var(--radius-lg);">
          <strong style="color:var(--teal); font-size: 1.25rem; display:block; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">ISO 14001 Certified</strong>
          <p style="font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.6; color:var(--ink-soft); margin:0;">
            Operating under rigorous international standards for environmental management, guaranteeing waste water recycling and emissions controls.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div style="background:var(--silver-soft); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding:2rem; border-radius:var(--radius-lg);">
          <strong style="color:var(--teal); font-size: 1.25rem; display:block; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Scrap Closed-Loop</strong>
          <p style="font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.6; color:var(--ink-soft); margin:0;">
            Re-smelting internal scrap and supporting buyer closed-loop programs to reintegrate clean manufacturing scrap directly into new billet casts.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div style="background:var(--silver-soft); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding:2rem; border-radius:var(--radius-lg);">
          <strong style="color:var(--teal); font-size: 1.25rem; display:block; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">REACH Compliance</strong>
          <p style="font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.6; color:var(--ink-soft); margin:0;">
            All alloy elements are completely free of SVHCs (Substances of Very High Concern), meeting the strictest European chemical purity criteria.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       FINAL CTA
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="final-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow on-dark">CBAM Support Desk</span>
      <h2>Secure a verified low-carbon allocation</h2>
      <p>Talk to Noel Murphy today to receive verified carbon density sheets or structure an annual low-carbon supply agreement.</p>
      <div class="final-cta-actions">
        <a href="/en/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">Request a Quote</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/353871187806" class="btn btn-secondary">Call Noel: +353 87 118 7806</a>
      </div>
      <p class="final-cta-direct">
        Direct Email: <a href="mailto:noel@egyptalumin.com">noel@egyptalumin.com</a> · WhatsApp: <a href="https://wa.me/353871187806">Direct Chat</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .product-img-container-inner {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 16/10;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }
  .product-img-modern {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
  }
  .product-img-container-inner:hover .product-img-modern {
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }
</style>
